<p><strong>Week 5 review:</strong> Month-3 churn prevention branch for novelty-fade cohort. Referral campaign creative with Marsello or native referral. Confirm collision calendar updated for upcoming peak weeks and that subscription, wholesale, or gift-buyer tags still suppress conflicting promos.</p>
<p><strong>Week 6 review:</strong> Postscript/Omnisend ship notification and skip deadline SMS. Quiet hours and opt-in audit. Confirm collision calendar updated for upcoming peak weeks and that subscription, wholesale, or gift-buyer tags still suppress conflicting promos.</p>
